This map was made in SDK Hammer, this is my second map for me it looks decent, for feedback don't forget comments, and if bots are stuck at spawn or like that put in console "nav_generate" i have already done that but if it wont saved then thats command  to use, this map took me 1 day to make, i'm pretty happy with that, enjoy ;)

1,) Open your CSS Folder
2,) Find folder named cstrike open it
3,) Find and open folder named "Maps"
4,)Put the bsp file inside
5,) Now launch game and enjoy ;)
